The Earth wind example includes baked NOAA GFS 10 m wind data retrieved through
NOAA ERDDAP, dataset ncep_global_lon180. Tropical cyclone markers are generated
from GDACS event data. Those data sources remain subject to their respective
providers' terms and attribution guidance.
